{"tid":1239270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請盡快檢查選民資格","createTime":"2019-06-18T06:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T13:04:01.000Z","uid":64689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"882ee67ee2e727a8ed469ba23fcaa41392299591","tid":1239270,"uid":64689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"以下係我同事選民登記資料，分分鐘冇得投超級區議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢冇換身份證，冇轉地址，亦未曾做過其他功能界別選民，但佢有可能唔記得登記做超級區議會選民<br />\n<br />\n因此盡快check check你同你父母嘅選民資料是否正確，一票都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/intro.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2Fintro.jsp&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=0c59c219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/intro.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287bf95e821f365c6a1680297d12e7a3a8fb5810","tid":1239270,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"fc70d2952a79867488b760e2bf970b3b66910f3c","tid":1239270,"uid":64689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3efe7e311970c5f75e237439f9567dfa468b9e32","tid":1239270,"uid":64689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06bb67c9d3b137e7689c77a438e145ac2a1d5027","tid":1239270,"uid":3632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"查唔到<br />\n每次入完資料 下一步都死link"},{"pid":"022c645577b894f984ddc60a493c88b42ceadf92","tid":1239270,"uid":64689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06bb67c9d3b137e7689c77a438e145ac2a1d5027","tid":1239270,"uid":3632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"查唔到<br />\n每次入完資料 下一步都死link"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"政府野戇鳩鳩<br />\n我都load咗勁耐先入到<br />\n試埋呢條link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2F&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=52302a2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/</a>"},{"pid":"99f62b445fc45175b096016be80061ed333a75bc","tid":1239270,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"係咪全香港都查緊？"},{"pid":"ef07f0fbe0b697c57fd8c8b1dfcd8d3cb3a0ac34","tid":1239270,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1e0fee0f0d49c745785e73144a562954ee9cf0da","tid":1239270,"uid":64689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:16:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5a2cc9a5be58e65852ccdafe3cc5a29d38abcf92","tid":1239270,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"［注意！］小心選民資格被取消？<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處已於2019 年12 月13 日以抽樣方式寄出查核信件，受查核選民需於2020年1 月31 日戓之前回覆，否則會被取消選民資格。<br />\n<br />\n收到信嘅朋友，最好回覆後，再打去確認，就萬無一失啦！<br />\n<br />\n無收到信嘅朋友，都唔好咁淡定！記得用下列方法，確認下自己有無被抽中：<br />\n1. 登入選民資料網上查閱系統，輸入個人資料後，如頁面下方有紅色字顯示（見附圖），即表示你被抽中<br />\n網址： <a href=\"http://www.voterinfo.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterinfo.gov.hk&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=f7a19251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.voterinfo.gov.hk</a><br />\n2. 致電選民熱缐組查詢，電話：28911001<br />\n<br />\n如發現被抽中，又收不到信，請立即致電選舉事務處28911001，要求跟進。<br />\n<br />\n根據選舉事務處資料：<br />\n上次抽様查核人數共25,892， 最終10,853位選民被取消資格（佔抽樣人數42%）<br />\n可想而知，唔少人都可能大意左，而被取消資格。今次抽様查核人數多達123,989人，佔選民人數成3%架，如果接近半成被取消，你話幾唔抵！<br />\n<br />\n#一票不能少 #搶攻立法會<br />\n#check信箱 #1月31前回覆 <br />\n#確認有否被抽中 ： <a href=\"http://www.voterinfo.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterinfo.gov.hk&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=f7a19251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.voterinfo.gov.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EYxThC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EYxThC.jpg&h=2e626bbf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}